                    <span>This book is a fantastic reference for Windows programmers.  However, as others below have mentioned, its fourth release is now available under the title "Programming Applications for Microsoft Windows."  If you're comfortable with Windows programming and are looking to get into some of the meatier areas, check it out.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Doing serious Win32 Development? YES. Then get this book.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
